README

It can be helpful to be able to easily configure a firewall.
The following provide some firewall basics:

1. Unified Firewall (UFW) on Linux
- Copy ufw-deuce-server to /etc/ufw/applications.d
- enable with: ufw allow DEUCE

2. IP-Tables on Linux
- iptables_deuce-server provides a rule that can be added to your rule list_ 
